DiD_data
========

This repository is a mirror of publicly distributed replication data files
used by the book "DiD and Beyond" (companion materials at
github.com/pedrohcgs/Econ-730---Causal-Panel-Data).

Each subdirectory's data files retain the license under which they were
originally distributed by the paper's authors or the journal's replication
archive. See the README.md file inside each subdirectory for the upstream
source URL and any author-supplied license note.

The directory structure, top-level README, and per-folder README files in
this repository are made available under Creative Commons CC0 1.0
Universal (public domain dedication). The data files themselves are NOT
relicensed by this repository.

Attribution: When citing the underlying datasets, cite the original
papers (citations in each per-folder README), not this mirror.
